high_descs: Walk passed the bed, turn left towards the middle of the bed and then turn right towards the desk.
Pick up the right white pen on the desk.
Place the pen in the black up on the desk.
Pick up the cup with the pen.
Turn left, walk towards the window, and then turn left towards the bedside table.
Place the cup to the left of the alarm clock.
anns.task_desc: Place a black cup with a pen on the bedside table.

high_descs: Go forward before turning left between the desk and bed and turning right towards the desk
Pick up the pen to the right and above the pencil on the desk
Place the pen in the mug that is to the right of the phone
Pick up the mug with the pen inside it
Turn around and go between the bed to the left and the wall to the right towards a small nightstand
Place the mug with the pen on the side table to the right of the bed and to the left of the clock
anns.task_desc: Placing a mug with a pen on a nightstand

high_descs: Walk ahead to the black desk.
Pick up the pen to the right of the other pen.
Place the pen in the black mug.
Turn around and veer right to the nightstand to the right of the bed.
Place the mug on the nightstand to the left of the alarm clock.
anns.task_desc: Place a mug with a pen in it on a night table.
